Theme_GreenDroid_Light

public static final int Theme_GreenDroid_Light
The following themes inherits from the Theme.Light Android base theme. They are strict copies of the previous themes which a large source of errors However, it looks like there are no way to overcome this (multiple inheritance is not permitted).
